Burst damage is under rated.
<br />

<br />
On a side note, I dont know who is telling you high end wizards only hit 150 sustained...that would be a seriously lazy and or gimp wizard.
<br />

<br />
DPS in general is a misleading and only moderately useful statistic when determining the viability of a class in a group.  It is a min/maxxer number used to justify a group makeup that they prefer, nothing more.
<br />

<br />
At the very high end of the game you will find pretty much everyone puts out enough damage to clear a given area so fast its not even funny, so who really cares if someone does 'more in 10 seconds of fighting' when your having to pull from 4 miles away to find something to kill.
