                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I also note that you left out Harvest of Druzzil, Mental Clarity and Devoted Familiar (or even the mana regen from a 'nuke' familiar. And your mana savings for SCM3 is lower than the traditionally accepted one. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
